Story ID: SPRINT1GRP1STORY0001


Feature: Book Browsing and Sorting

Title
Book Browsing and Sorting. As a book browser, I would like to have the ability to browse books in a way that it is easier to find the books I am looking for. Whether is new releases or A to Z. 
Status:
New
Acceptance Criteria
User can browse top sellers in our bookstore
User can browse by book rating
User can allow pagination based on 10 or 20 results
User can Sort by book title	
User can Sort by author
User can Sort by price
User can Sort by rating
User can Sort by date
Estimate
8 (hours)

